      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. Can you expand a bit more on the psychological side of things? Like, how do these attackers actually manipulate people's emotions to get them to bypass standard security protocols? I want to emphasize the \"trickery\" aspect in the training so employees understand it's not just about tech errors, but intentional manipulation.",
